title: H.S. BOYS SOCCER: Binkowski scores with five seconds left, secures double OT victory for B-H | Game | thedailynewsonline.com
text:
BATH — The Bath-Haverling boys soccer team hosted Livonia on Monday night, coming away with a thrilling 1-0 victory after scoring with five seconds left in double overtime.
The late goal was scored by Conner Binkowski, off an assist by Caleb Lyke.
